  "description": "Create a fully constrained 2D sketch of an L-shaped building perimeter with a uniform 150mm wall thickness. The outer perimeter must be anchored at the origin (0,0) with the following dimensions: left edge (6000mm vertical), top edge (3000mm horizontal), inner vertical edge (2000mm), inner horizontal edge (2000mm), rightmost edge (4000mm vertical), and bottom edge (5000mm horizontal). The inner perimeter must maintain a constant 150mm offset from the outer walls. Save the final sketch to ~/Documents/SolveSpace/l_shape_floor_plan.slvs.",
